# Normalize EOL for all files Git considers text; binaries are auto-detected.
* text=auto eol=lf

# No Git LFS. This project is text-authored with only a few MB of generated
# assets (PNG backdrops/sprites, MP3/WAV audio) committed directly. The
# previous LFS config anticipated heavy 3D models (.fbx/.blend/…) that the
# procedural, no-imported-models pipeline never produces. Committing the
# small assets as plain blobs avoids the LFS-pointer mismatch that appears
# when the repo is cloned somewhere LFS is installed.
